
 Member of the Steering Committee 
  
  Responsible for collecting both loan repayments and savings for members during the bi-weekly meetings where monney.

Responsible for holding group money until distributions, deposits, or payments are made.

Once money is collected the secretary documents the transaction. (SHARED)

Treasurer must either be elected by unanimous vote, or appointed by the President/s (Group Loan Underwriter/s)

Treasurer is intedned to be non-partisan and the objective decider in a comittee vote.

Potential credit check is required? Single or continous? In line with Presidents'?

